main event: One observer reported seeing a bright luminous light-object in Jacksonville, Florida on August 25, 1967.
interesting points: The object appeared fuzzy around the edges,The observer viewed the object through 8X binoculars,The object disappeared by growing dim and blinking out,It was estimated that the object was slightly larger than a match head,The object was described as being disc-shaped and bright white.
witness description: 14-year-old male who reported to the police.
